        NO_MATTER_HOW_HARD_I_TRY_MY_LOUSY                                       = 10612,  -- No matter how hard I try, my lousy husband will never be more than a weak, cowardly, whining mutt...
        HM_OH_NOT_ANOTHER_ADVENTURER_I_APPRECIATE_ALL                           = 10613,  -- Hm? Oh, not another adventurer... I appreciate all the aid coming in from Jeuno, but I miss the peace and quiet of the old Tavnazia. With all the scruffy travelers constantly coming up to me asking for this and that, I can't concentrate on my daily chores!
