        YES_I_TOO_HAVE_SEEN_THE_SIMILARITIES_BETWEEN                            = 11315,  -- Yes, I, too, have seen the similarities between Prishe and the adventurers who pass through our gates. Their courage and ambition never cease to amaze me.
