        A_TRULY_SKILLED_ADVENTURER_KNOWS_WHEN_HE_IS                             = 11324,  -- A truly skilled adventurer knows when he is outmatched.
        YES_BUT_I_WOULDN_T_HAVE_BEEN_OUTMATCHED                                 = 11325,  -- Yes, but I wouldn't have been outmatched if I were more like Prishe...
        WITH_THE_PASSING_OF_EACH_DAY_I_SEE                                      = 11326,  -- With the passing of each day, I see the people around me growing stronger, while I remain the same.
        IT_IS_OFTEN_EASY_TO_WITNESS_CHANGE_IN                                   = 11327,  -- It is often easy to witness change in others, never realizing that you, too, are transforming as well.
        BUT                                                                     = 11328,  -- But...
        DO_YOU_THINK_THAT_I_HAVE_NOT_SPENT                                      = 11329,  -- Do you think that I have not spent hours, days, standing here pondering over the same trivial issues? I know how you feel, Parelbriaux. However, your situation is not as dire as you may believe it to be.
        BUT_ENOUGH_OF_THIS_IDLE_CHAT_YOU_SHOULD                                 = 11330,  -- But enough of this idle chat. You should have someone tend to your wounds.
        WHAT_OF_CHEMIOUE_SHE_IS_ONE_OF_THE                                      = 11331,  -- What of Chemioue? She is one of the finest physicians we have.
        I_DON_T_KNOW_IF_THAT_S_SUCH                                             = 11332,  -- I don't know if that's such a good idea...
        WHAT_DO_NOT_TELL_ME_YOU_TWO_HAD                                         = 11333,  -- What? Do not tell me you two had another one of your arguments.
        IT_WASN_T_REALLY_AN_ARGUMENT_IT_WAS                                     = 11334,  -- It wasn't really an argument. It was more like...well... Yes, we had an argument. And you know how she can be when she's rubbed the wrong way.
        NOW_THAT_YOU_MENTION_IT_IT_MIGHT_NOT                                    = 11335,  -- Now that you mention it, it might not be so wise to go to her right away...considering I used some of the medicine in her bag on your cuts.
        EVEN_THOUGH_IT_IS_CHEMIOUE_WHO_SHOULD_BE                                = 11336,  -- Even though it is Chemioue who should be more careful with her possessions, if she finds out that I opened her pack without permission, she'll have my head on a plate!
        CAREFUL_WITH_HER_POSSESSIONS                                            = 11337,  -- Careful with her possessions...
        YES_CHEMIOUE_DROPPED_HER_BAG_WHEN_SHE_CAME                              = 11338,  -- Yes. Chemioue dropped her bag when she came running through the Porte d'Esmodille.
        DROPPED_WHEN_RUNNING_OH_NO_THEY_RE_GONE                                 = 11339,  -- Dropped...when running... Oh no! They're gone!
        I_MUST_HAVE_DROPPED_THEM_WHILE_RUNNING_FROM                             = 11340,  -- I must have dropped them while running from that monster!
        WHAT_ARE_YOU_RAMBLING_ON_ABOUT_MAN                                      = 11341,  -- What are you rambling on about, man?
        THE_PETALS_FROM_A_RARE_VARIETY_OF_FLOWER                                = 11342,  -- The petals--from a rare variety of flower that only grows in the Lufaise Meadows.
        WE_READ_SOMEWHERE_THAT_THEY_ARE_SUPPOSED_TO                             = 11343,  -- We read somewhere that they are supposed to have remarkable healing properties. She thought that if we could find one and bring it back to the safehold, we could help all the sick children...
        HMMM_IF_WE_HURRY_THERE_MIGHT_STILL_BE                                   = 11344,  -- Hmmm... If we hurry, there might still be some petals left where you found the others. However, you are too injured to leave the safehold, and I cannot leave my post... Quite a predicament, I say.
        AH_WHAT_ABOUT_THIS_ADVENTURER                                           = 11345,  -- Ah! What about this adventurer?
        I_REALIZE_THAT_YOU_ARE_BUSY_WITH_YOUR                                   = 11346,  -- I realize that you are busy with your adventuring escapades, but could you lend us your services, if only for a few moments?
        IT_WOULD_MEAN_THE_WORLD_TO_PARELBRIAUX_IF                               = 11347,  -- It would mean the world to Parelbriaux if you could run out and retrieve one of those petals of which he was speaking.
        AND_IF_NOT_FOR_HIM_DO_IT_FOR                                            = 11348,  -- And if not for him, do it for the safehold's dying children...
        PLEASE_FINE_SIR_LADY_YOU_ARE_OUR_ONLY                                   = 11349,  -- Please, fine sir/lady]. You are our only hope.
        WELCOME_BACK_IS_THAT_THE_ITEM_PARELBRIAUX_WAS                           = 11350,  -- Welcome back, %. Is that the item Parelbriaux was searching for? Quite an odor, I must say.
        HM_HAVE_I_SEEN_CHEMIOUE_WHY_YES_SHE                                     = 11351,  -- Hm? Have I seen Chemioue? Why, yes. She passed by here a few moments ago. However, she ran by so quickly, I was unable to ask her the details of her journey.
        CHEMIOUE_WHAT_S_WRONG_YOU_LOOK_LIKE_YOU                                 = 11352,  -- Chemioue? What's wrong? You look like you just ran from the far side of the island.
        THESE_CUTS_OH_THEY_RE_NOT_AS_BAD                                        = 11353,  -- These cuts? Oh, they're not as bad as they--
