        WHO_DO_YOU_THINK_YOU_ARE_TRYING_TO                                      = 11355,  -- Who do you think you are trying to impress with this macho act? Now stop acting like a buffoon and show me your wounds.
        YOU_RE_NOT_STILL_MAD_AT_ME_ARE                                          = 11356,  -- You're not still mad at me, are...hm? This ointment... It smells like...
        WELL_IT_IS_SAFE_TO_SAY_THAT_YOUR                                        = 11357,  -- Well, it is safe to say that your nose was not injured during your little adventure. You are correct. This ointment is made from the flowers that grow in Lufaise. An adventurer was generous enough to give me one of his/hers] when I was out in the meadows.
