        WHO_AH_IT_S_YOU_I_NEVER_KNOW                                            = 12043,  -- Who...? Ah, it's you, %. I never know when one of you adventurers will choose to darken my doorstep.
        IT_MAY_NOT_BE_MY_PLACE_TO_SAY                                           = 12044,  -- It may not be my place to say it, but Prishe seemed upset with you.
        YOU_SEE_I_FOUND_THIS_UNUSUAL_RING_ON                                    = 12045,  -- You see, I found this unusual ring on one of my patrols. When I showed it to Prishe and Ulmia, they were certain it was the same ring they gave to you.
        POOR_ULMIA_SEEMED_ON_THE_VERGE_OF_TEARS                                 = 12046,  -- Poor Ulmia seemed on the verge of tears. Is this how you treat a person's heartfelt gift!?
        IT_MIGHT_BE_NOTHING_MORE_THAN_A_BAUBLE                                  = 12047,  -- It might be nothing more than a bauble to you, but for those girls it was a symbol of your friendship--your unbreakable bond!
        HERE_TAKE_IT_MAYBE_THIS_TIME_YOU_LL                                     = 12048,  -- Here, take it. Maybe this time you'll think twice about how much it's really worth...
        GREETINGS_FRIEND_I_AM_A_SYNERGY_ENGINEER_DISPATCHED                     = 12049,  -- Greetings, friend! I am a synergy engineer, dispatched from the Institute to maintain the furnaces you see beside me. I also have knowledge and services to share with fellow synergists, if that is what you desire.
        I_SEE_FROM_THE_PUZZLED_EXPRESSION_ON_YOUR                               = 12050,  -- I see from the puzzled expression on your face that you are unfamiliar with our discipline. To use these furnaces, you will first need to obtain %.
        PIQUED_YOUR_CURIOSITY_HAVE_I_THEN_YOU_SHOULD                            = 12051,  -- Piqued your curiosity, have I? Then you should speak with Hildolf, our institute director, at his laboratory in the Bastok Metalworks. He's always eager to welcome a new synergist to our ranks.
        MAY_I_BE_OF_SERVICE_NOT_NOW_LEARN                                       = 12052,  -- May I be of service? Not now. Learn recipes. Check fewell. Replenish fewell. Purchase materials. Receive training. Trade cinder. Get information.
        RECIPES_YOU_SAY_LET_S_SEE_WHAT_WE                                       = 12053,  -- Recipes, you say? Let's see what we have that's suitable for your level of expertise...
        I_M_SORRY_I_M_AFRAID_THERE_S                                            = 12054,  -- ...I'm sorry. I'm afraid there's nothing I can teach you at the moment.
        I_VE_GOT_IT_HOW_ABOUT_MIND_YOU                                          = 12055,  -- I've got it! How about %? Mind you, it'll require a certain level of skill...
