        IF_YOU_HAVE_SUCH_AN_ITEM_THAT_YOU                                       = 12259,  -- If you have such an item that you're simply dying to entrust to me, you'll have to abandon your trial first, kupo.
        AND_THAT_S_ALL_THERE_IS_TO_IT                                           = 12260,  -- And that's all there is to it. This humble moogle can hardly wait to serve you!
