        I_VE_BEEN_DISPATCHED_FROM_MANY_MALMS_AWAY                               = 13076,  -- I've been dispatched from many malms away on a very important mission.
        WHAT_MIGHT_THAT_OBJECTIVE_BE_YOU_ASK_ONE                                = 13077,  -- What might that objective be, you ask? One as heroically challenged as you need not concern yourself with it.
        I_VE_BEEN_DISPATCHED_FROM_MANY_MALMS_AWAY_2                             = 13078,  -- I've been dispatched from many malms away on a very important mission. What sort of mission, you ask? An astute question indeed! And here I'd begun to lose hope of meeting any capable adventurers in these provincial backwaters.
        SHHH_NOT_SO_LOUD                                                        = 13079,  -- (Shhh! Not so loud!)
        YES_I_HAIL_FROM_JEUNO_BUT_WE_CAN                                        = 13080,  -- (Yes, I hail from Jeuno, but we can't let the riffraff around these parts be privy to that information.)
        WHAT_EXACTLY_IS_MY_OBJECTIVE_OH_COME_NOW                                = 13081,  -- What exactly is my objective? Oh, come now. I'm certain a hero/a heroine] of your caliber could figure it out. The secrecy, the mention of <cough> Jeuno <cough>, propositioning adventurers...
        YES_IT_DOES_INDEED_INVOLVE_VOIDWALKERS_THOSE_EERIE                      = 13082,  -- Yes, it does indeed involve Voidwalkers--those eerie menaces that traverse time and space by way of those planar rifts. I haven't the foggiest idea as to why, but they've apparently decided to make Tavnazia their next battlefront.
        I_WAS_GIVEN_AN_ORDER_TO_DISPOSE_OF                                      = 13083,  -- I was given an order to dispose of the threat, effective immediately. However, these fishmongering philistines...how do I put this politely? Show no respect for the Voidwatch's jurisdiction.
        NO_MATTER_HOW_CIVIL_I_TRY_TO_BE                                         = 13084,  -- No matter how civil I try to be around these country bumpkins, they simply won't let me do my job. Thus I've been secretly recruiting adventurers to aid in our cause.
        WHAT_SAY_YOU_TAKE_PITY_ON_A_FELLOW                                      = 13085,  -- What say you take pity on a fellow crusader of justice and help rid this wasteland of its interdimensional intruders?
        OH_SO_YOU_RE_I_VE_HEARD_MUCH                                            = 13086,  -- Oh, so you're %? I've heard much about you from Justinius.
        ONE_OF_THOSE_BEING_THAT_YOUR_EXPLOITS_FACTORED                          = 13087,  -- One of those being that your exploits factored heavily in Jeuno's decision to trade with this region.
        IN_THAT_SENSE_ONE_COULD_SAY_IT_S                                        = 13088,  -- In that sense, one could say it's your doing--for better or worse--that I've been dispatched to this goddess-forsaken crag.
        I_HAVE_A_PROPOSITION_BUT_I_WARN_YOU                                     = 13089,  -- I have a proposition, but I warn you--this task is more harrowing than listening to your mother-in-law berate you over a deceptively cordial cup of tea about how you don't spend enough time with your wife. Even now, I can see her eyes...bearing into my soul...as her venomous tongue paralyzes me like a death jacket's stinger. Die! Die, you accursed fiend!
        BUT_I_DIGRESS_THIS_MISSION_ACTUALLY_INVOLVES_VOIDWALKERS                = 13090,  -- But I digress. This mission actually involves Voidwalkers. According to the Tavnazian Patrol, planar rifts have been opening up across the archipelago recently.
        WHAT_THEY_SEE_IN_THIS_PIDDLING_SWATH_OF                                 = 13091,  -- What they see in this piddling swath of scattered rocks, I haven't a clue.
        STILL_IF_THEY_CAN_FIND_A_MOUND_OF                                       = 13092,  -- (Still, if they can find a mound of rubble like Tavnazia habitable, what's stopping them from infesting every area in the realm?)
        IN_SUMMATION_WE_NEED_YOUR_ASSISTANCE_IN_EXTERMINATING                   = 13093,  -- In summation, we need your assistance in exterminating these pests.
        WHAT_DO_YOU_SAY_WILL_YOU_DO_YOUR                                        = 13094,  -- What do you say? Will you do your part for the Voidwatch?
        WHAT_WILL_YOU_DO_NOTHING_AT_ALL_ASK                                     = 13095,  -- What will you do? Nothing at all. Ask many a question. Participate in Voidwatch Ops. Request debriefing. Request %. Check voidstone stock. Request reward issuance.
        I_SEE_IT_WOULD_SEEM_EVERYONE_IN_THESE                                   = 13096,  -- I see... It would seem everyone in these parts is a lily-livered craven. It must be something in the water...
        WHOA_WHOA_WHOA_THERE_S_SOMETHING_I_NEED                                 = 13097,  -- Whoa, whoa, whoa! There's something I need to get off my chest. I figured no one in this dirthole would be brave enough to sign up, so I didn't bother reading the recruitment manual.
        IT_PAINS_ME_TO_ADMIT_MY_OWN_IGNORANCE                                   = 13098,  -- It pains me to admit my own ignorance, but you'll have to seek out a Voidwatch Officer if you want some answers.
        DID_YOU_FINALLY_GROW_A_BACKBONE_NOW_ARE                                 = 13099,  -- Did you finally grow a backbone? Now are you ready to join the Voidwatch and make the realm proud?
        PEOPLE_SAY_I_SOUND_LIKE_A_POMPOUS_JACKANAPES                            = 13100,  -- People say I sound like a pompous jackanapes, but at least I know how to give thanks. Your help will be more than welcome in the Uleguerand Range, Lufaise Meadows, Attohwa Chasm, and on the Misareaux Coast.
        YOU_LL_NEED_THIS_FOR_YOUR_OPERATIONS_AS                                 = 13101,  -- You'll need this % for your operations as well. Take it. Don't hold back on my account.
        HOWEVER_THIS_WON_T_BE_OF_MUCH_USE                                       = 13102,  -- However, this won't be of much use unless you're also in possession of %...or so my superiors tell me. Very well then. May you save the realm and one day depart this bastion of boors.
        REMEMBER_YOU_CAN_ALWAYS_COME_TO_ME_FOR                                  = 13103,  -- Remember, you can always come to me for help should backcountry life prove too stressful. If nothing else, we can always bemoan our terrible fates together.
        YOU_HAVE_YET_TO_COMPLETE_ALL_OF_YOUR                                    = 13104,  -- You have yet to complete all of your objectives. Proceed to [Lufaise Meadows/Misareaux Coast/Uleguerand Range/Attohwa Chasm][, Misareaux Coast/, Uleguerand Range/, Attohwa Chasm/ for your final task./][, Uleguerand Range/, Attohwa Chasm/, Misareaux Coast/][, and Attohwa Chasm.//Victory is nearly in our grasp!/, and...yes, that is all.] I wish you the best of luck.
        VOIDWALKERS_HAVE_REAPPEARED_AT_LUFAISE_MEADOWS_MISAREAUX_COAST          = 13105,  -- Voidwalkers have reappeared at Lufaise Meadows, Misareaux Coast, Uleguerand Range, [and Attohwa Chasm/Attohwa Chasm, and Bibiki Bay]. Keep your chin up! With your help, we'll put an end to this Voidwalker invasion yet! ...I hope.
        MY_COMPATRIOTS_WITHIN_THE_WATCH_TELL_ME_THAT                            = 13106,  -- My compatriots within the 'Watch tell me that you've exterminated every last threat to the archipelago. Admirably done.
        BUT_WE_BOTH_KNOW_THE_OLD_ADAGE_ABOUT                                    = 13107,  -- ...But we both know the old adage about assuming. Only greenhorns and village idiots fail to realize that these creatures possess an uncanny ability to revive as if they'd never suffered a scratch. If only we could decipher the manner in which they cheat death...
        STAY_THAT_THOUGHT_IF_VOIDWALKERS_CAN_RESURRECT_THEN                     = 13108,  -- Stay that thought... If Voidwalkers can resurrect...then my mission will never end! I don't want to be trapped on this isolated archipelago for eternity! What will my hydrangeas ever do without me!?
        WAIT_I_HAVE_AN_IDEA_YOU_KNOW_WHAT                                       = 13109,  -- ...Wait, I have an idea! You know what might turn the tide of this fathomless bloodbath? A war of attrition! If you could return every so often to slay these undying anomalies, we might yet be able to terminate the Voidwalkers once and for all!
        WERE_YOU_AWARE_THAT_THE_INHABITANTS_OF_THIS                             = 13110,  -- Were you aware that the inhabitants of this land finally decided to open trade with Jeuno?
        THOUGH_I_OFTEN_SPEAK_ILL_OF_THEM_TRUTH                                  = 13111,  -- Though I often speak ill of them, truth is the locals are rather open-minded and accepting, though a tad unsophisticated.
        EVEN_JUSTINIUS_OF_THE_TAVNAZIA_PATROL_HAS_PROVEN                        = 13112,  -- Even Justinius of the Tavnazia Patrol has proven quite cooperative.
        SPEAKING_OF_JUSTINIUS_IT_WOULD_BEHOOVE_US_TO                            = 13113,  -- Speaking of Justinius, it would behoove us to inform him of your victories.
        YOU_RE_A_CREDIT_TO_ADVENTURERS_EVERYWHERE_JUSTINIUS                     = 13114,  -- You're a credit to adventurers everywhere. Justinius certainly knows a capable man/woman] when he sees one. Speaking of Justinius, it would behoove us to inform him of your victories.
        I_LL_TELL_YOU_WHERE_I_LL_PUT                                            = 13115,  -- I'll tell you where I'll put my hooves if you're gonna keep secrets from me!
        I_KNEW_YOU_COULD_DO_IT_NO_ONE                                           = 13116,  -- I knew you could do it, %! No one can come close to matching your awesomeness!
        MISAREAUX_MANTRAPS_WHO_MIGHT_YOU_BE                                     = 13117,  -- Misareaux mantraps! Who might you be!?
        I_SEE_YOU_RE_AT_IT_AGAIN_WE                                             = 13118,  -- I see you're at it again, %. We all know how powerful you are, so how about throwing the patrol a bone every once in a while? We're dying for some good press!
        JUSTINIUS_HAS_TOLD_ME_ALL_ABOUT_YOUR_EXPLOITS                           = 13119,  -- Justinius has told me all about your exploits. You're always there for Tavnazia when it needs you, %. Thanks.
        ALTHOUGH_I_GUESS_IT_SHOULD_ONLY_BE_A                                    = 13120,  -- Although, I guess it should only be a matter of time before we get our due, what with all the Voidwalkers crawling around Tavnazia lately.
        BUT_VOIDWALKERS_TEND_TO_REAPPEAR_LIKE_MAGGOTS_ON                        = 13121,  -- But Voidwalkers tend to reappear like maggots on meat, right?
        JUST_YOU_WAIT_WE_LL_CUT_DOWN_SO                                         = 13122,  -- Just you wait! We'll cut down so many of those mystical invaders that...well, there won't be any left for you!
        MAYBE_THIS_S_THE_TAVNAZIAN_PATROL_S_CHANCE                              = 13123,  -- Maybe this's the Tavnazian Patrol's chance to get some good press of our own!
        PRISHE_THIS_IS_HARDLY_THE_TIME_TO_BE                                    = 13124,  -- Prishe! This is hardly the time to be engaging in idle chatter! Your studies await!
        YIKES_FOR_CRYING_OUT_LOUD_ULMIA_YOU_VE                                  = 13125,  -- Yikes! For crying out loud, Ulmia, you've become more of a curmudgeon than Despachiaire!
        ULMIA_2                                                                 = 13126,  -- Ulmia!
        ANYWAY_I_LL_SEE_YOU_LATER                                               = 13127,  -- Anyway, %, I'll see you later!
        I_GUESS_I_VE_BEEN_CORRALLED_SEE_YOU                                     = 13128,  -- I guess I've been corralled... See you around.
        THAT_GIRL                                                               = 13129,  -- That girl...
        IT_S_WONDERFUL_TO_SEE_YOU_IN_SUCH                                       = 13130,  -- It's wonderful to see you in such high spirits, %. I always knew in my heart of hearts that we would meet again.
        AS_YOU_CAN_SEE_PRISHE_IS_AS_LIVELY                                      = 13131,  -- As you can see, Prishe is as lively as she's ever been.
        WHO_KNOWS_WHERE_SHE_I_AND_ALL_OF                                        = 13132,  -- Who knows where she, I, and all of Tavnazia would be without you, %. Please return to visit us again sometime. Preferably after Prishe's lessons are finished.
        WELL_WELL_WELL_I_SHOULD_HAVE_KNOWN_THAT                                 = 13133,  -- ...Well, well, well. I should have known that being an adventurer is about having gil and dames/beaus] scattered all over the realm.
