        WHY_SHE_S_SO_EMBARRASSED_ABOUT_ALTER_EGOS                               = 13233,  -- Why she's so embarrassed about alter egos is beyond me. She can sure belt out a tune, so imagine a full ensemble of six or seven Ulmias!
        YOU_ACTUALLY_GOT_HER_TO_GO_ALONG_WITH                                   = 13234,  -- You actually got her to go along with it!?
        I_DIDN_T_THINK_YOU_HAD_IT_IN                                            = 13235,  -- I didn't think you had it in you! She was so flustered by the whole thing, I figured she'd crumble at the mere suggestion of it. Well done, pal!
        BUT_LET_S_GET_BACK_TO_WHAT_MATTERS                                      = 13236,  -- But let's get back to what matters--your relationship with me.
        I_WAS_ONLY_VAGUELY_PAYING_ATTENTION_TO_THE                              = 13237,  -- I was only vaguely paying attention to the damned lecture the institute gave me, but they said something about bonds of friendship and trust being the key.
        TRUST_HAH_WE_VE_GOT_SO_MUCH_MORE                                        = 13238,  -- Trust? Hah! We've got so much more than that.
        AFTER_ALL_WHICH_DYNAMIC_DUO_SAVED_THE_WORLD                             = 13239,  -- After all, which dynamic duo saved the world from ruin at the hands of Promathia?
        IF_I_COULDN_T_TRUST_YOU_WHY_WOULD                                       = 13240,  -- If I couldn't trust you, why would I let you out of my sight for a minute? No, it's more than trust--it's destiny!
        AH_CRAP_BUT_THERE_S_MORE_TO_IT                                          = 13241,  -- Ah, crap...but there's more to it than that. There's also friendship, too.
        NOW_THAT_I_THINK_ABOUT_IT_I_REMEMBER                                    = 13242,  -- Now that I think about it, I remember a time when some old jeweler over in Jeuno was going on and on about what love really is.
        YOU_KNOW_WHAT_I_LEARNED_FROM_HIM_THAT                                   = 13243,  -- You know what I learned from him? That love ain't something you know about until it hits you. So that means I don't know what love is?
        BUT_I_RECALL_SHARING_SOMETHING_WITH_A_CERTAIN                           = 13244,  -- But I recall sharing something with a certain young girl...
        ANIMALS_HAVE_HEARTS_AND_SOULS_JUST_LIKE_PEOPLE                          = 13245,  -- Animals have hearts and souls, just like people do, and their hearts are much more pure than ours.
        NOW_IF_ONLY_I_WERE_AS_PURE_AS                                           = 13246,  -- Now if only I were as pure as a moogle, then maybe...
        AH_SCREW_IT_ALL_WHAT_S_THIS_WEIRD                                       = 13247,  -- Ah, screw it all! What's this weird heat coming from my cheeks?
        THE_TWO_OF_US_MAKE_ONE_HELL_OF                                          = 13248,  -- [Well, then/Hmm... Come to think of it], the two of us make one hell of a team, don't you agree?
        ALTHOUGH_A_CERTAIN_SOMEONE_YELLED_AT_ME_NOT                             = 13249,  -- Although a certain someone yelled at me not to leap without looking all the time.
        LET_ME_SHARE_WITH_YOU_A_LITTLE_SOMETHING                                = 13250,  -- Let me share with you a little something. There's this geezer over in Jeuno, always with his fishing rod by the docks, who musta stared daggers at me for hours on end.
        YOU_D_PICTURE_HE_D_VE_JUST_TOLD                                         = 13251,  -- You'd picture he'd've just told me to be careful, but oh no!
        IF_IT_WERE_YOU_IN_A_PIT_OF                                              = 13252,  -- If it were you in a pit of snakes, though, I wouldn't care what any old fart would have to say! I'd throw myself in after you in a heartbeat!
        TWO_OF_US_CAN_LICK_ANY_PROBLEM_BIG                                      = 13253,  -- [Well, the/Let's continue. The] two of us can lick any problem, big or small.
